description:
Seth Rogen [Superbad, Pineapple Express, An American Pickle]  is an actor, comedian, writer, producer, and director. Seth talks with Anna about his new movie An American Pickle, lying to the press, wishing he could sing, taking a long ocean voyage, getting high on Mars and more. Then Dan Savage from Savage Lovecast is back to provide some more qualified advice as he and Anna talk with Chris.
